    "description": "Deckarium 是一个构建牌组的宠物模拟器。玩宠物卡片，将宠物添加到你的玻璃容器地或水族馆，并通过关卡解锁新卡片加入你的牌组。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/694a639e42f65598f2afaa2a7551541c.apng?t=1768357779\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/694a639e42f65598f2afaa2a7551541c.poster.avif?t=1768357779\" class=\"bb_img\" width=90 height=75 /></picture></span><br><br>保持你的宠物吃得好，它们会为你生产硬币。有些宠物的胃口比其他的更大！如果你想从更大的宠物中受益，你将不得不维持食物链。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/27700f685ada3eb939f4c61cb1c15cb1.apng?t=1768357779\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/27700f685ada3eb939f4c61cb1c15cb1.poster.avif?t=1768357779\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=100 /></picture></span><br><br>你的宠物不是唯一的饥饿者！小心那些只想吞噬你宠物灵魂的幽灵！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/581d64cbb21435d9b4abdaa6df001b6a.apng?t=1768357779\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/581d64cbb21435d9b4abdaa6df001b6a.poster.avif?t=1768357779\" class=\"bb_img\" width=140 height=220 /></picture></span><br><br>通过关卡和小游戏赚取额外货币，用于你个人的闲置玻璃容器地和水族馆，在那里你可以收集并命名自己独特的宠物，而无需担心幽灵！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/07c97cd372bfa1a8d39bafa3c02248e5.apng?t=1768357779\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/07c97cd372bfa1a8d39bafa3c02248e5.poster.avif?t=1768357779\" class=\"bb_img\" width=110 height=70 /></picture></span>",
